Description: ===============================
        hardware
        ===============================
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/enovance/hardware.svg?branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.org/enovance/hardware
        
        Hardware detection and classification utilities
        
        Features
        --------
        
        * detect hardware features of a Linux systems:
        
          * RAID
          * hard drives
          * IPMI
          * network cards
          * DMI infos
          * memory settings
          * processor features
        
        * filter hardware according to hardware profiles
        
        
